text: kraoyomk pitabrakd nasa mcheasa robsa anakchea anak chuoy dl banda anak del ban phiesakhluon( chenhpi mea kkah) kraoypi puokke trauv ban ke thveutoukkh bok me nnh banteabmk puokke ban tsaou(knong meakra robsa a l laoh) ning ban atthmot . pitabrakd nasa mcheasa robsa anak ku mha aphytosa mha anet sraleanh kraoypi kar sarphap kamhosa robsa puokke
